{"lemma":"فِضَّة","slug":"فِضَّة","root":"ف.ض.ض","root_slug":"ف-ض-ض","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ض-ض","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فِضَّة","root":"فضض","pos":"N","occurrence_count":6},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34029","n34035","n34036"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B6%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"silver","tags":["uncountable"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/fidˤ.dˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34029","headword_ar":"فَضَّهُ","root":"fD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafuD~u","text_ar":"يَفُضُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~N","text_ar":"فَضٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, O, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, the seal (A, Mgh, Msb, K) of a letter; (A, K;) and any other thing; (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he broke it asunder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into several pieces; he dissundered it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, K;) for instance, the seal from a letter. (S, O.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faS~a AlxaAtama","text_ar":"فَصَّ الخَاتَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a metonymical phrase, meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inivit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [or rather,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. a."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~ AlbakaArapa","text_ar":"فَضّ البَكَارَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he destroyed the virginity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the virginity being likened to a seal, or this phrase is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faDaDotu All~uw^oluw^apa","text_ar":"فَضَضْتُ اللُّوْلُوَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I bored,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforated, the pearl."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [See also 8.] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~a A@ll~`hu faAhu","text_ar":"فَضَّ ا@للّٰهُ فَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) and, accord. to IKtt, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afaD~ahu","text_ar":"اَفَضَّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which J disallows, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God broke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God break, his teeth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God scattered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may God scatter, his teeth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yafoDuDi A@ll~`hu faAka","text_ar":"لَا يَفْضُضِ ا@للّٰهُ فَاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A.) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God not break thy teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) occurs in a trad.: (S, A:) and J says. (TA,) you should not say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yufoDiD","text_ar":"يُفْضِض","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA; [but in"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2409},{"kind":"text","text":"one copy of the S, I find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafoDiD","text_ar":"يَفْضِض"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) though some allow it: and some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoDaA'","text_ar":"اـِفْضَاء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[evidently a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoDaAD","text_ar":"اـِفْضَاض"},{"kind":"text","text":"] means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falling out"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the teeth"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from above and below;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but the former explanation is the more common. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He separated it; dispersed it; scattered it; broke it up;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, TA;) namely, a thing; (Msb;) or a party of men; (S, O;) or a ring of men, (A, TA,) after they had collected together. (TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~a AlmaAla EalaY Alqawomi","text_ar":"فَضَّ المَالَ عَلَى القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, * TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He distributed the property among the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party of men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA. *) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faDaDotu maA bayonahumaA","text_ar":"فَضَضْتُ مَا بَيْنَهُمَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I cut"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tie,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bond, that was between them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~a AlmaA='a","text_ar":"فَضَّ المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor. and] inf. n. as above,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He poured out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forth, the water;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~umuwEa","text_ar":"الدُّمُوعَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tears."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 57.) [See also 8.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~a AlmaA='u","text_ar":"فَضَّ المَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor., accord. to rule,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yafiD~u","text_ar":"يَفِضُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water flowed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~umuwEu","text_ar":"الدُّمُوعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnfD~t","text_ar":"انفضّت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tears poured forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 57.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","A","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n34035","headword_ar":"فَضَّةٌ","root":"fD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n34036","headword_ar":"فِضَّةٌ","root":"fD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Silver;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain thing well known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrought silver:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T and K voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tiborN","text_ar":"تِبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiDaDN","text_ar":"فِضَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawaAriyra","text_ar":"قَوَارِيرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino fiD~apK","text_ar":"مِنْ فِضَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [lxxvi. 16], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flasks"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"notwithstanding their clearness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transparency, will be secure from being broken, and capable of being restored to a sound state if broken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like silver:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O,) being, as Zj says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"originally of silver, yet transparent, so that what will be within them will be seen from without;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whereas the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qwAryr","text_ar":"قوارير"},{"kind":"text","text":"of this world are originally from sand. (Az, O.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qr","text_ar":"قر"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An elevated"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stony tract such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~ap","text_ar":"حَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~apN","text_ar":"فَضَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiDaDN","text_ar":"فِضَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiDaADN","text_ar":"فِضَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ibn- 'Abbád, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiDaADu AljibaAli","text_ar":"فِضَاضُ الجِبَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rocks scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manovuwr","text_ar":"مَنْثُور"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano$uwr","text_ar":"مَنْشُور"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one upon another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, O, K:) sing. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~apN","text_ar":"فَضَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Az"]}]}}